  {
    "uuid": "92906ad4-d4d5-5312-98b5-5c5a0d00044e",
    "entry": "速弁",
    "reading": {
      "primary": "はやべん",
      "alternatives": [],
      "is_heteronym": false
    },
    "grammar": {
      "pos": [
        "名詞"
      ],
      "ctype": null,
      "inflections": null
    },
    "definitions": [
      {
        "index": 1,
        "gloss": "boxed lunch sold at highway rest areas",
        "register": "standard",
        "nuance": null,
        "scenarios": [],
        "sensory_tags": {
          "colors": [],
          "temperature": null,
          "sounds": [],
          "emotions": []
        },
        "collocations": [],
        "examples": {
          "standard": [
            {
              "text": "長距離ドライブの途中、サービスエリアで人気の速弁を買った。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-2.5-flash"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "この速弁は、地元の食材をふんだんに使っていて美味しい。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-2.5-flash"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "昔は速弁の種類が少なかったが、今は多種多様で選ぶのが楽しい。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-2.5-flash"
              }
            }
          ],
          "literary": [
            {
              "text": "私は博文館で懲り懲りしていますから早速弁護士を頼んで掛合って貰い先今日までのところでは別に損害は受けていません。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "出版屋惣まくり",
                "author": "永井荷風",
                "note": "青空文庫"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "もはやべんべんとそれを待ってはいられない。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "渡良瀬川",
                "author": "大鹿卓",
                "note": "青空文庫"
              }
            }
          ]
        }
      }
    ],
